fficiency, lightweight yet durable design, quick-charge ability and balance between performance and ease of use make it a true achievement. The XR advances our product range and the foiling world in general.<\/p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3.jpg\" alt=\"Stoke XR Battery back view\" class=\"wp-image-5469 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2240\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3.jpg\" alt=\"Stoke XR Battery back view\" class=\"wp-image-5469 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3.jpg 2240w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-60x34.jpg 60w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/3-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2240px) 100vw, 2240px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure><\/div><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your downwinding experience with the Stoke Foil XR Battery<\/h2><p>Let&#8217;s use the art of downwinding as an example case for the XR Battery. Extended battery life allows you to cover greater distances and explore expansive stretches of water. Downwinding relies on harnessing the energy within the water, and the XR Battery assists in this dynamic practice. Connect the bumps and foil freely with the power to ride the waves gracefully and precisely.<\/p><p>Foiling enthusiasts cherish the feeling of the endless glide, and the XR Battery ensures that this remains uninterrupted. Crafted with a lightweight design, our battery adds minimal weight to your setup, allowing you to maintain the agility and responsiveness essential for navigating through the dynamic conditions of downwinding.<\/p><p>Whether you prefer prone with a chip in the wave, using a wing, or the classic paddle method, the XR Battery adapts to your foiling style. While iconic downwinding locations like Hawaii, Western Australia, and Hood River are dream destinations, the XR Battery unlocks the potential for downwinding anywhere with a large enough body of water to generate bumps. European waterways, landlocked locations, and even Dutch lakes become your playground as the XR Battery empowers you to explore beyond the traditional downwinding hotspots.<\/p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2.jpg\" alt=\"Stoke XR Battery Side View\" class=\"wp-image-5468 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2240\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2.jpg\" alt=\"Stoke XR Battery Side View\" class=\"wp-image-5468 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2.jpg 2240w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/2-60x34.